  <brief_title>Safety Study of GS-5806 to Treat Respiratory Syncytial Virus (RSV)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1b, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Single-Dose Ranging Study Evaluating the Safety, Tolerability, and Pharmacokinetics of GS-5806 in Subjects &lt; 24 Months of Age Hospitalized for Respiratory Syncytial Virus (RSV) Related Respiratory Infection</official_title>
  <sponsors>
